data.description: Welcome home to your 3 bedroom / 2.5 bathroom townhome recently built in 2016! The home features modern finishes including granite counter tops, recessed lighting, Air Conditioning and heat along with ample garage space fitting up to two SUVs. Uniquely positioned at a corner lot and close to 905 and 805 freeways. Upon entering the family area, you'll be welcomed by abundant natural light that elegantly brightens the entire living space. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an ideal environment for daily living and entertaining. With only one shared wall with the neighboring property, you'll enjoy enhanced privacy and reduced noise, providing a peaceful living experience. As the larger model, this home boasts a larger square footage than most townhomes in the community, offering ample space for customization, whether you need a home office, a dedicated gym, or extra storage. Your options are endless. VA and FHA approved Complex with amenities that include playgrounds, swimming pool and spa!
